{"title":"谒焦裕禄墓","authors":["李锐锋"],"dates":[{"year":1990,"month":1,"day":23}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"谒焦裕禄墓"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"李锐锋"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"绿绿的泡桐"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你无言"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"悠悠的云彩"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你无言"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你坐在无言的碧石上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"脚下的黄沙"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"奔流而去"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我为你轻弹身上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"斑驳的碱屑"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"棉花絮和豆角的皮屑"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从你肩上落下"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我问候你"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你沉默着——微微一笑"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"河坝上的涛声"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"和着这座小城"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"年轻的步子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也一起涌来"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我站起身"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你站起身"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你只是直挺挺地站着"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这土地如此坚实"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"她感觉到你的脚步"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如五月的麦穗一样沉重"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我一直看着你"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你正和一个伟人交谈"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他挥手就写了几个"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"光辉灿烂的大字＊"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你笑了——看着它"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"直到很远"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"很远"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"*焦裕禄墓坐落在河南兰考县城北河岗上，墓后是水泥墙壁，上面有毛泽东的题词：“为人民而死，虽死犹荣”"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}